r.sub.i =W.sub.i L/|F|
where ri is the average number of patterns having the feature to be learned that can be seen by the recognition element, Wi is a count of the total number of patterns having the feature to be learned that can be seen by the recognition element, L is a learning constant, and |F| is a count of the total number of patterns having the feature to be learned.
